sectionText: Restricted to online non-degree, online MCS, online MSME and online MS CE students. CS certificate students must take this course for 4 hours.  Counts toward a certificate in Computer Science. For more details on this course section, please see http://online.engineering.illinois.edu/current-students/course-information/spring-2013-credit-course-offerings.
